	(text "SW Up -> Detector Return Shorted Directly to Ground, -5V off\nSW Down -> Detector Return shorted to -5V, ground disconnected\nNeeds to be DPDT - ON-ON Configuration, no middle state\nEnsures exlusive control to ensure that we never short -5V to ground"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 247.65 158.75 0)
		(effects
