				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "eb32e747-f53e-4493-9f34-cccc7469df0b")
	)
	(text "Main Power Supply\n\nConsists of a Boost Converter to 24.5V, \nfollowed by the HRC05. It also Consists of a \nBuck Converter to 5.5V, which is then regulated,\nto both a +5.0V and -5.0V rail. The -5.0V is, of\ncourse, meant to be the float/detector return path.\nThe +5.0V is meant to supply the digital\nlogic, that being the arduino, the ADC's and DAC, \nthe and the controls"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 113.03 80.01 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
			)
		)
		(uuid "fefd6eea-7daf-423f-91bb-19736634a1d1")
	)
